---
import { Card } from "@/components/ui/card";
---

<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#0D2845]">Strategies That Fit Your Needs</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Managing your finances can feel overwhelming. When you're thinking about your family's future, it's hard to know where to start. The cookie-cutter advice most people receive just doesn't cut it when your financial needs are unique and complex.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
      <div class="flex items-center">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600880292089-90a7e086ee0c?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"
          alt="Financial planning session"
          class="rounded-lg shadow-xl"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Without a clear, personalized strategy, it's easy to make costly mistakes or miss opportunities that could significantly improve your financial situation. Not knowing whether you're on the right path can take a serious toll on your peace of mind and your future plans.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            That's where we come in. With our personalized financial planning approach, we'll get a strategy that is as unique as you are. We take the time to understand your goals and financial concerns. We can craft a plan tailored specifically to you, to ensure advice and expert guidance and clear direction.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <Card class="p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553729459-efe14ef6055d?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"
          alt="Build Your Wealth"
          class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
        />
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0D2845]">Build Your Wealth</h3>
      </Card>
      <Card class="p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1454165804606-c3d57bc86b40?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"
          alt="Grow Your Wealth"
          class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
        />
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0D2845]">Grow Your Wealth</h3>
      </Card>
      <Card class="p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579621970563-ebec7560ff3e?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"
          alt="Protect Your Wealth"
          class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
        />
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0D2845]">Protect Your Wealth</h3>
      </Card>
      <Card class="p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1434626881859-194d67b2b86f?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"
          alt="Protect Your Legacy"
          class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
        />
        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#0D2845]">Protect Your Legacy</h3>
      </Card>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>